Shard of Sloth
Source Pathfinder #61: Shards of Sin pg. 69 (Amazon)
Aura overwhelming conjuration CL 25th
Slot none; Price â€”; Weight 1 lb.
Description:
The Shard of Sloth is made of blue-green glowing abysium. As long as the Shard of Sloth is carried, its owner can use summon monster III as a spell-like ability once per day, gains a +2 insight bonus on saves versus conjuration spells, and gains a +4 insight bonus on all concentration and caster level checks.

Curse:
You are Mildly Drowsy - no save
Movement speed halved.
DC20 Will save per turn.  Failure=No Standard Immediate actions.
After being awake for 1 hour:
  DC15 Will vs Sleep.  Success buys another hour.
  Failure means you Sleep for 25 minutes, as per https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic/all-spells/s/sleep
  This sleep does not count as a Rest.  You may still long-rest at your leisure.
